1
00:00:18,208 --> 00:00:20,000
- Natsu:
PREVIOUSLY, ON "FAIRY TAIL"...

2
00:00:20,083 --> 00:00:21,958
- Happy: IT WAS TOUGH,
BUT OUR BAND OF HEROES

3
00:00:22,041 --> 00:00:24,375
FINALLY BEAT THE ORACION SEIS
AND NIRVANA.

4
00:00:24,458 --> 00:00:26,250
GO TEAM!
 - Lucy: UNFORTUNATELY,

5
00:00:26,333 --> 00:00:28,458
THE SWEET TASTE OF VICTORY
TURNED BITTER

6
00:00:28,541 --> 00:00:31,250
AS WE WERE FORCED
TO SAY GOODBYE TO DEAR FRIENDS.

7
00:00:32,458 --> 00:00:35,625
- ( theme music playing )

8
00:00:48,750 --> 00:00:51,125
- ( singing in Japanese )

9
00:02:08,625 --> 00:02:10,875
- Ultear: MASTER HADES.

10
00:02:10,958 --> 00:02:12,875
I'M SORRY TO DISTURB YOU,
MY LORD.

11
00:02:12,958 --> 00:02:15,500
- Hades: IS IT AS I EXPECTED?

12
00:02:15,583 --> 00:02:17,250
- IT IS INDEED, MASTER.

13
00:02:17,333 --> 00:02:19,083
THE ORACION SEIS HAVE FALLEN

14
00:02:19,166 --> 00:02:22,000
AND NIRVANA WAS DESTROYED
BY THE OFFICIAL GUILDS.

15
00:02:22,083 --> 00:02:25,583
- THE COALITION WAS AS CAPABLE
AS I'D ANTICIPATED.

16
00:02:25,666 --> 00:02:27,708
OUR OBJECTIVE
REMAINS UNHINDERED.

17
00:02:27,791 --> 00:02:30,666
- YES, SIR. NIRVANA'S
DESTRUCTION IS BUT A RIPPLE

18
00:02:30,750 --> 00:02:32,833
IN THE VAST SEA OF OUR SCHEME.

19
00:02:32,916 --> 00:02:34,333
IT WON'T BE LONG
BEFORE WE POSSESS

20
00:02:34,416 --> 00:02:36,541
THE KEYS TO ZEREF'S SEAL.

21
00:02:36,625 --> 00:02:37,791
HOWEVER--

22
00:02:37,875 --> 00:02:40,375
- DO NOT TRY MY
PATIENCE, ULTEAR.

23
00:02:40,458 --> 00:02:43,125
- NIRVANA'S DESTRUCTION
MAY SERVE AS THE HERALD

24
00:02:43,208 --> 00:02:45,250
OF AN EVEN
GREATER DISTURBANCE.

25
00:02:45,333 --> 00:02:48,166
SO GREAT, IN FACT, THAT IT WILL
RENDER OUR GOALS UNREACHABLE

26
00:02:48,250 --> 00:02:49,625
IF LEFT UNCHECKED.

27
00:02:49,708 --> 00:02:52,666
- ( chuckles )
NOW THIS IS ENTERTAINING.

28
00:02:52,750 --> 00:02:54,708
YOU AREN'T AFRAID, ARE YOU?

29
00:02:54,791 --> 00:02:58,041
- NOT AT ALL,
I'M LOOKING FORWARD TO IT.

30
00:03:01,833 --> 00:03:04,875
- AH! SO THIS IS WHAT IT'S LIKE
TO SAIL THE SEAS

31
00:03:04,958 --> 00:03:06,833
WITHOUT PUKING
YOUR BRAINS OUT.

32
00:03:06,916 --> 00:03:08,833
- AYE, MATEY,
WELCOME TO THE GOOD LIFE.

33
00:03:08,916 --> 00:03:11,250
- HA HA!
LOOK OUT, VEHICLES.

34
00:03:11,333 --> 00:03:13,250
NATSU'S GONNA RIDE YOU HARD.
- CAREFUL!

35
00:03:13,333 --> 00:03:15,375
THE TROIA SPELL
DOESN'T LAST FOREVER.

36
00:03:15,458 --> 00:03:17,291
- FOR THOSE OF YOU
WHO MIGHT NOT KNOW,

37
00:03:17,375 --> 00:03:19,875
TROIA IS A HEALING SPELL
THAT CURES MOTION SICKNESS.

38
00:03:19,958 --> 00:03:23,416
- ARGH! NO.
CAST THAT SPELL AGAIN.

39
00:03:23,500 --> 00:03:25,500
HURRY.
- I'M SORRY, I CAN'T.

40
00:03:25,583 --> 00:03:27,583
IT ONLY WORKS
A COUPLE OF TIMES.

41
00:03:27,666 --> 00:03:30,666
- GUESS IT'S BACK TO BARF BAGS.
- ( laughs )

42
00:03:30,750 --> 00:03:32,750
- WHEN YOU AND WENDY
JOIN FAIRY TAIL,

43
00:03:32,833 --> 00:03:35,375
I'LL SHOW YOU ALL THE SNUGGLING
SPOTS PERFECT FOR KITTIES.

44
00:03:35,458 --> 00:03:37,500
- I'M JOINING YOUR GUILD
TO STAY CLOSE TO WENDY,

45
00:03:37,583 --> 00:03:39,208
NOT BECAUSE I HAVE ANY INTEREST
IN YOU.

46
00:03:39,291 --> 00:03:42,666
- WE'RE JOINING FAIRY TAIL!
THIS IS SO EXCITING.

47
00:03:47,583 --> 00:03:50,125
- ( Happy speaking )

48
00:03:52,875 --> 00:03:55,750
- Lucy: WITH A HARD-FOUGHT
BATTLE NOW BEHIND US,

49
00:03:55,833 --> 00:03:58,166
IT'S FINALLY TIME
TO RETURN TO HOME.

50
00:03:58,250 --> 00:04:01,958
- MAN!  MAY YOUR PARFUMS
GRACE MY NOSTRILS AGAIN,

51
00:04:02,041 --> 00:04:04,250
MISS ERZA AND MISS LUCY.

52
00:04:04,333 --> 00:04:06,833
- BE SURE TO COME VISIT US
WHENEVER YOU FEEL LIKE IT.

53
00:04:06,916 --> 00:04:09,000
- WHEN YOU DO, BE READY
FOR THE BEST NIGHT

54
00:04:09,083 --> 00:04:10,250
BLUE PEGASUS CAN OFFER.

55
00:04:10,333 --> 00:04:13,125
- GIVE MY WARMEST REGARDS
TO MASTER MAKAROV.

56
00:04:13,208 --> 00:04:15,625
- OH, AND GRAY,
FIX THAT STRIPPING HABIT.

57
00:04:15,708 --> 00:04:17,875
- LIKE YOU HAVE
ANY ROOM TO TALK, YOU BONEHEAD!

58
00:04:17,958 --> 00:04:19,250
- QUESTION.

59
00:04:19,333 --> 00:04:21,666
WHAT DO WE DO
ABOUT THOSE TWO?

60
00:04:21,750 --> 00:04:23,791
- WELL, AREN'T YOU RUNNING
OFF WITH YOUR LITTLE FRIENDS?

61
00:04:23,875 --> 00:04:26,208
- YEAH, AND JUST SO YOU KNOW,
I'M NOT GONNA MISS YOU.

62
00:04:26,291 --> 00:04:27,833
- SHERRY.
- REN.

63
00:04:27,916 --> 00:04:30,291
- THEY'RE SO IN LOVE!

64
00:04:30,375 --> 00:04:34,125
- Lucy: IT'S CERTAINLY BEEN
A WILD RIDE, MOM.

65
00:04:37,541 --> 00:04:39,708
OH, AND YOU'LL NEVER GUESS
WHAT HAPPENED.

66
00:04:39,791 --> 00:04:41,958
I GOT
THREE NEW CELESTIAL KEYS.

67
00:04:42,041 --> 00:04:43,625
- Gemi: ANGEL'S LOCKED UP,

68
00:04:43,708 --> 00:04:45,416
SO NOW OUR CONTRACTS WITH HER
ARE NULL AND VOID.

69
00:04:45,500 --> 00:04:46,750
- Mini: THAT'S RIGHT.

70
00:04:46,833 --> 00:04:48,250
- NOW THAT WE'RE FREE.

71
00:04:48,333 --> 00:04:50,208
WE'VE ALL DECIDED
THE BEST PERSON

72
00:04:50,291 --> 00:04:52,000
TO TAKE OVER OUR CONTRACTS
WOULD BE NONE OTHER THAN YOU,

73
00:04:52,083 --> 00:04:53,916
LUCY HEARTFILIA.
WICKED!

74
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:56,750
- WOULD YOU PLEASE BE OUR
WIZARD? - Both: PIRI-PIRI.

75
00:04:56,833 --> 00:04:59,458
- SO YOU REALLY WANT
TO FORM CONTRACTS WITH ME?

76
00:04:59,541 --> 00:05:01,250
ARE YOU GUYS SURE ABOUT THIS?

77
00:05:01,333 --> 00:05:02,958
YOU "GUYS"?

78
00:05:03,041 --> 00:05:04,875
- WE'RE JUST USED
TO BEING CALLED PETS

79
00:05:04,958 --> 00:05:06,500
AFTER WORKING WITH ANGEL
ALL THIS TIME.

80
00:05:06,583 --> 00:05:07,791
- I KNOW.

81
00:05:07,875 --> 00:05:10,041
BUT THAT DOESN'T WORK FOR ME.

82
00:05:10,125 --> 00:05:12,125
I THINK
OF MY SPIRITS AS EQUALS.

83
00:05:12,208 --> 00:05:14,750
YOU'RE NO DIFFERENT TO ME
THAN MY GUILD MATES.

84
00:05:14,833 --> 00:05:16,583
YOU'RE LIKE FAMILY.

85
00:05:16,666 --> 00:05:18,166
- HMMM!

86
00:05:18,250 --> 00:05:20,250
- IT WOULD BE OUR PLEASURE
TO WORK WITH YOU, LUCY.

87
00:05:20,333 --> 00:05:21,708
- Both: PIRI-PIRI.

88
00:05:21,791 --> 00:05:24,250
- I HOPE WE'RE TOGETHER
FOR A LONG TIME,

89
00:05:24,333 --> 00:05:27,458
SCORPIO, GEMINI AND ARIES.

90
00:05:27,541 --> 00:05:31,250
NEW FRIENDS ARE COMING
INTO MY LIFE IN DROVES.

91
00:05:31,333 --> 00:05:32,833
AND I COULDN'T BE HAPPIER!

92
00:05:32,916 --> 00:05:35,333
- Erza: LONG STORY SHORT--

93
00:05:35,416 --> 00:05:38,041
WENDY AND CARLA ARE
FAIRY TAIL'S NEWEST MEMBERS,

94
00:05:38,125 --> 00:05:39,875
SO YOU'D BETTER
TREAT THEM WELL.

95
00:05:39,958 --> 00:05:41,958
- IT'S A PLEASURE
TO MEET YOU ALL.

96
00:05:42,041 --> 00:05:44,375
- ADORABLE! - LOOK
THERE'S EVEN A FEMALE HAPPY.

97
00:05:44,458 --> 00:05:45,875
- I BET YOUR MOM'S
REAL PRETTY!

98
00:05:45,958 --> 00:05:48,375
- WE'RE SO GLAD YOU MADE IT
BACK SAFELY.

99
00:05:48,458 --> 00:05:51,291
- HELLO, MASTER.

100
00:05:51,375 --> 00:05:53,291
- GREAT WORK, ERZA.

101
00:05:53,375 --> 00:05:55,375
I'M SURE THINGS
WILL QUIET DOWN

102
00:05:55,458 --> 00:05:58,041
NOW THAT THE ORACION SEIS
ARE OUT OF THE PICTURE.

103
00:05:58,125 --> 00:06:00,083
AND THANKS FOR BRINGING
TWO PRECIOUS

104
00:06:00,166 --> 00:06:02,208
YET POWERFUL ADDITIONS
TO THE GUILD BACK WITH YOU.

105
00:06:04,833 --> 00:06:06,416
- GIRL,
IT'S BEEN TOO LONG!

106
00:06:06,500 --> 00:06:09,125
- YOU'RE TELLING ME.
- HUG ATTACK!

107
00:06:09,208 --> 00:06:11,750
- AWW.  NOW THAT'S AN ATTACK
I'LL ALWAYS TAKE.

108
00:06:11,833 --> 00:06:13,208
- DOES LUCY
SEEM DIFFERENT TO YOU?

109
00:06:13,291 --> 00:06:14,791
- KIND OF.

110
00:06:14,875 --> 00:06:16,958
WHO KNOWS WHAT CRAZINESS
SHE HAD TO GO THROUGH?

111
00:06:17,041 --> 00:06:18,666
- ( crashing )
- Both: OH!

112
00:06:18,750 --> 00:06:21,083
- GRAY, DARLING.
YOU'RE BACK!

113
00:06:21,166 --> 00:06:23,041
I'M SO HAPPY
YOU MADE IT HOME.

114
00:06:23,125 --> 00:06:25,416
MY TEARS ARE FLOWING
LIKE WATERFALLS!

115
00:06:25,500 --> 00:06:27,875
- GRAY. STOP YOUR GIRLFRIEND,
MAN, WE'RE DYING HERE!

116
00:06:27,958 --> 00:06:29,666
- SHE'S NOT
MY FREAKIN' GIRLFRIEND!

117
00:06:32,125 --> 00:06:34,250
- AND THEN THE GIANT SNAKE
SPROUTED WINGS

118
00:06:34,333 --> 00:06:35,500
AND STARTED FLYING!

119
00:06:35,583 --> 00:06:37,041
- YEAH, YEAH, NOW I KNOW
YOU'RE PULLING MY LEG.

120
00:06:37,125 --> 00:06:38,750
SNAKES AREN'T MANLY ENOUGH
TO FLY.

121
00:06:38,833 --> 00:06:39,833
- YOU SAW IT.

122
00:06:41,333 --> 00:06:43,208
- WELCOME TO FAIRY TAIL,
YOU TWO.

123
00:06:43,291 --> 00:06:44,708
I'M MIRAJANE.
- WOW!

124
00:06:44,791 --> 00:06:46,125
I CAN'T BELIEVE
THIS IS HAPPENING.

125
00:06:46,208 --> 00:06:48,250
FIRST I MET ERZA,
NOW MISS MIRAJANE.

126
00:06:48,333 --> 00:06:50,166
- I'M GUESSING YOUR FELINE
FRIEND USES

127
00:06:50,250 --> 00:06:51,500
THE SAME MAGIC AS HAPPY.

128
00:06:51,583 --> 00:06:54,125
YOU MIND TELLING US
WHAT TYPE OF MAGIC YOU USE?

129
00:06:54,208 --> 00:06:55,791
- WAIT A MINUTE.

130
00:06:55,875 --> 00:06:58,041
DON'T YOU DARE COMPARE ME
TO THAT FURRY HORN DOG!

131
00:06:58,125 --> 00:06:59,583
- DON'T MIND HER.

132
00:06:59,666 --> 00:07:01,541
I USE HEALING
AND SUPPORT MAGIC.

133
00:07:01,625 --> 00:07:03,833
ACTUALLY,
I'M A SKY DRAGON SLAYER.

134
00:07:03,916 --> 00:07:05,291
- ( all gasping )

135
00:07:09,458 --> 00:07:12,333
- DID I DO SOMETHING WRONG
ALREADY?

136
00:07:12,416 --> 00:07:15,000
- All: THAT'S AWESOME!

137
00:07:16,416 --> 00:07:18,750
WE HAVE
ANOTHER DRAGON SLAYER!

138
00:07:18,833 --> 00:07:22,000
- AW, YEAH!
- JUST LIKE NATSU AND GAJEEL!

139
00:07:22,083 --> 00:07:23,833
- I'VE NEVER HEARD OF A GUILD
WITH THREE DRAGON SLAYERS IN IT!

140
00:07:23,916 --> 00:07:25,750
WE'RE GONNA BE
EVEN MORE UNSTOPPABLE NOW.

141
00:07:25,833 --> 00:07:27,708
- WELCOME TO THE FAMILY.
HAPPY TO HAVE YOU ABOARD.

142
00:07:33,791 --> 00:07:36,833
- ( both meowing )

143
00:07:38,083 --> 00:07:40,916
- IT'S NOT FAIR.

144
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:42,625
SERIOUSLY!

145
00:07:42,708 --> 00:07:45,000
I MEAN
I'M A DRAGON SLAYER TOO.

146
00:07:45,083 --> 00:07:49,125
WHEN DO I GET
MY OWN FLYING KITTY CAT, HUH?

147
00:07:49,208 --> 00:07:51,541
- ALL RIGHT EVERYONE,
LISTEN UP!

148
00:07:51,625 --> 00:07:54,958
LET'S WELCOME OUR NEW MEMBERS
THE WAY ONLY FAIRY TAIL CAN!

149
00:07:56,750 --> 00:07:59,916
NOW, EAT, DRINK,
AND MAKE MERRY!

150
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:02,125
YEAH!
WHO WANTS TO BRAWL?

151
00:08:02,208 --> 00:08:04,750
- AH!  LOOK AT ME
AND YOU LOSE AN EYE.

152
00:08:04,833 --> 00:08:06,458
OH YEAH?
WELL, IT'D BE WORTH IT, BABY.

153
00:08:06,541 --> 00:08:08,291
- DARLING, ARE YOU CHEATING
ON ME WITH THAT TRAMP?

154
00:08:08,375 --> 00:08:10,208
- HUH?
WHAT ARE YOU TALKIN' ABOUT?

155
00:08:10,291 --> 00:08:12,041
- YOU KNOW, CARLA, IF YOU EAT
A FISH WITH A LOVED ONE,

156
00:08:12,125 --> 00:08:13,916
YOU'LL HAVE GOOD LUCK.
- THAT IS NOT YOU.

157
00:08:21,041 --> 00:08:23,916
- EVERYONE IS SO LIVELY
AND FILLED WITH HAPPINESS.

158
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:25,666
- KEEP YOUR GUARD UP, CHILD.

159
00:08:38,666 --> 00:08:40,916
- MMM.

160
00:08:47,500 --> 00:08:50,083
- HAS ANYTHING ON THE BOARD
CAUGHT YOUR INTEREST?

161
00:08:50,166 --> 00:08:52,375
- THERE'RE SO MANY,
IT'S HARD TO PICK ONE.

162
00:08:52,458 --> 00:08:54,125
- TAKE YOUR TIME.

163
00:08:54,208 --> 00:08:56,166
THOUGH, IF YOU WOULDN'T MIND
A LITTLE ADVICE,

164
00:08:56,250 --> 00:08:58,125
I'D STAY AWAY
FROM SOLO JOBS FOR NOW.

165
00:08:58,208 --> 00:09:00,291
SINCE YOU'RE
JUST STARTING OUT,

166
00:09:00,375 --> 00:09:02,041
IT MIGHT BE BEST TO ASSIST
ANOTHER TEAM

167
00:09:02,125 --> 00:09:03,208
WITH ONE OF THEIR JOBS.

168
00:09:03,291 --> 00:09:04,708
- YOU'LL TAKE A PAY CUT,
OF COURSE,

169
00:09:04,791 --> 00:09:06,875
BUT THE EXPERIENCE
IS WELL WORTH IT.

170
00:09:06,958 --> 00:09:08,791
- SOUNDS LIKE A LOT OF FUN.

171
00:09:08,875 --> 00:09:10,333
- I ADMIRE YOUR ENTHUSIASM,

172
00:09:10,416 --> 00:09:12,416
BUT TAKE A LOOK
AT YOUR POTENTIAL PARTNERS.

173
00:09:12,500 --> 00:09:14,750
- ( both laughing )

174
00:09:14,833 --> 00:09:16,916
- ( squealing )

175
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:18,916
- NOT A CHANCE.

176
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:21,083
- HELPING WENDY FIND A GOOD JOB,
MIRAJANE?

177
00:09:21,166 --> 00:09:23,833
- ACTUALLY, I THINK IT'D BE
BEST FOR HER TO TAG ALONG

178
00:09:23,916 --> 00:09:25,958
ON SOMEONE ELSE'S JOB
AND GET SOME EXPERIENCE.

179
00:09:26,041 --> 00:09:28,333
- GOOD PLAN.  I MEAN, LU-LU HERE
GOT HER START IN FAIRY TAIL

180
00:09:28,416 --> 00:09:30,416
BY HELPING NATSU, RIGHT?

181
00:09:30,500 --> 00:09:32,375
- AND IT'S LED ME INTO MORE
HORRIFYING AND DEADLY SITUATIONS

182
00:09:32,458 --> 00:09:34,375
THAN ANY GIRL
SHOULD HAVE TO ENDURE.

183
00:09:34,458 --> 00:09:36,500
- YOU'VE GOT MORE COURAGE
THAN ME, THAT'S FOR SURE.

184
00:09:36,583 --> 00:09:38,125
- COURAGE.

185
00:09:38,208 --> 00:09:40,625
WELL, THEN,
SINCE THE TWO OF YOU ARE HERE,

186
00:09:40,708 --> 00:09:43,083
IS THERE ANY WORK
THAT YOU NEED HELP WITH?

187
00:09:43,166 --> 00:09:44,583
I MAY STILL BE PRETTY GREEN,

188
00:09:44,666 --> 00:09:46,833
BUT I PROMISE
TO DO MY VERY BEST.

189
00:09:46,916 --> 00:09:49,458
- WE COULD REALLY USE THAT KIND
OF ATTITUDE IN SHADOW GEAR.

190
00:09:49,541 --> 00:09:51,666
- YOU WORKED WITH US BEFORE,
SO WHY NOT STICK AROUND?

191
00:09:51,750 --> 00:09:54,041
- UHH, SOMEHOW I THINK STICKING
WITH YOUR LITTLE GANG

192
00:09:54,125 --> 00:09:55,750
MIGHT BE BAD FOR HER HEALTH.

193
00:09:55,833 --> 00:09:57,750
- ( laughs )

194
00:09:57,833 --> 00:09:59,958
- WHY NOT HAVE HER WORK
WITH BOTH TEAMS?

195
00:10:00,041 --> 00:10:01,541
- GOOD IDEA.

196
00:10:01,625 --> 00:10:03,750
- SO WHICH TEAM
GETS YA FIRST?

197
00:10:03,833 --> 00:10:05,250
- HMM.

198
00:10:08,541 --> 00:10:10,208
- YO, NATSU.

199
00:10:10,291 --> 00:10:11,916
- YEAH, WHAT IS IT?

200
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:14,291
- Elfman:
WHERE'VE YOU BEEN HIDING, MAN?

201
00:10:14,375 --> 00:10:17,916
I HAVEN'T SEEN YOU FOR DAYS.
DID YOU TAKE A VACATION?

202
00:10:18,000 --> 00:10:20,833
- WHAT'S WRONG, MY LOVE?
YOU SEEM RATHER TROUBLED.

203
00:10:20,916 --> 00:10:25,291
- WHEN I WAS ON MY WAY HERE
I HEARD SOMETHING CRAZY.

204
00:10:25,375 --> 00:10:27,750
- AND THAT WOULD BE?

205
00:10:27,833 --> 00:10:31,333
- THE RUMOR MILL'S RUNNING
PRETTY HARDCORE AROUND TOWN.

206
00:10:31,416 --> 00:10:34,375
APPARENTLY THERE'S BEEN
A DRAGON SIGHTING.

207
00:10:37,083 --> 00:10:40,000
- Happy: SOMEONE SAW A DRAGON?
FOR REAL?

208
00:10:40,083 --> 00:10:43,041
- OKAY.
YOU'VE GOT MY ATTENTION.

209
00:10:43,125 --> 00:10:45,625
WAS IT IGNEEL?

210
00:10:45,708 --> 00:10:49,000
- I DIDN'T HEAR ANY NAMES,
SPECIFICALLY.

211
00:10:49,083 --> 00:10:51,458
- ALL RIGHT. DID YOU
AT LEAST TALK TO THE GUY

212
00:10:51,541 --> 00:10:53,750
WHO SAID HE SAW THIS DRAGON?
- NO.

213
00:10:53,833 --> 00:10:55,833
LIKE I SAID,
IT'S JUST A RUMOR I HEARD.

214
00:10:55,916 --> 00:10:57,791
APPARENTLY THE PERSON
WHO STARTED IT,

215
00:10:57,875 --> 00:11:00,583
SOME WOMAN NAMED DAPHNE,
SAYS THERE'S MORE TO THE STORY.

216
00:11:00,666 --> 00:11:02,833
ACCORDING TO HER,
SHE DIDN'T JUST SEE IT.

217
00:11:02,916 --> 00:11:06,083
SHE SAYS SHE ACTUALLY SPOKE
WITH THE DRAGON.

218
00:11:06,166 --> 00:11:09,208
- LIKE, IN PERSON?
IS IT TRUE, GRAY?

219
00:11:09,291 --> 00:11:12,583
