TO YOUR REPUTATION.

434
00:20:27,041 --> 00:20:29,583
- SHE'S KIND OF SCARY
WITHOUT HER TWANG.

435
00:20:29,666 --> 00:20:31,791
- I'M SO GLAD THAT ALL OF YOU
COULD MAKE IT.

436
00:20:31,875 --> 00:20:34,291
GOOD THINGS REALLY DO COME
TO THOSE WHO WAIT.

437
00:20:34,375 --> 00:20:36,250
- THIS WAS JUST A SET-UP.

438
00:20:36,333 --> 00:20:38,750
- YES YES YES!
AND YOU FELL RIGHT IN IT!

439
00:20:38,833 --> 00:20:40,875
SO SIT BACK AND HAVE SOME
METAMO-CHAN.

440
00:20:40,958 --> 00:20:42,125
- WHY WOULD I WANT THAT?

441
00:20:42,208 --> 00:20:44,250
- PERHAPS YOU'D LIKE
THE STRAWBERRY FLAVOR?

442
00:20:44,333 --> 00:20:46,791
- THERE'S ALSO WASABI
AND TERIYAKI. - I SAID NO!

443
00:20:46,875 --> 00:20:48,291
- WE CAN'T GO OUT HERE EITHER.

444
00:20:48,375 --> 00:20:50,750
- SEEMS THIS TRAP
WAS MASTERFULLY CRAFTED.

445
00:20:50,833 --> 00:20:53,958
- YES YES YES.
MY MAGIC IS QUITE SPLENDID.

446
00:20:54,041 --> 00:20:57,458
- I'VE NEVER MET A WALL
I COULDN'T BRING DOWN BY FORCE.

447
00:20:57,541 --> 00:21:00,291
AHHH!

448
00:21:00,375 --> 00:21:02,000
- AH!  NATSU!

449
00:21:05,041 --> 00:21:06,916
- WHAT THE--

450
00:21:09,750 --> 00:21:12,041
- HOW'S THE FLOOR FEEL,
NATSU?

451
00:21:12,125 --> 00:21:13,875
- OH, IT'S GRAY!
- WAIT.

452
00:21:13,958 --> 00:21:16,208
HOW WERE YOU ABLE TO GET PAST
THAT MAGIC WALL?

453
00:21:16,291 --> 00:21:17,708
- GOOD QUESTION.

454
00:21:17,791 --> 00:21:19,791
AND I'VE GOT MY OWN BONE
TO PICK WITH YOU.

455
00:21:19,875 --> 00:21:22,166
NEXT TIME MAKE SURE YOUR INFO
ISN'T COMPLETE GARBAGE.

456
00:21:22,250 --> 00:21:25,416
- HMMM.
IT WASN'T GARBAGE.

457
00:21:26,916 --> 00:21:29,083
YOU DID JUST WE WANTED.

458
00:21:29,166 --> 00:21:30,625
- YES YES YES, THEY DID.

459
00:21:30,708 --> 00:21:34,125
SO GLAD YOU COULD MAKE IT,
MY BELOVED GRAY.

460
00:21:34,208 --> 00:21:38,208
- YOU KNOW HER?
WHAT IS GOING ON, MAN?

461
00:21:38,291 --> 00:21:40,625
- ( laughs )

462
00:21:40,708 --> 00:21:43,041
- WHOA!
I THINK THEY'RE IN LOVE!

463
00:21:43,125 --> 00:21:45,166
- YOU'RE REALLY SLUMMIN' IT
IF YOU'RE WITH THIS CHICK.

464
00:21:45,250 --> 00:21:46,958
- SHUT UP.

465
00:21:47,041 --> 00:21:49,000
IF YOU DIDN'T THINK
THIS WAS GONNA HAPPEN ONE DAY,

466
00:21:49,083 --> 00:21:51,250
YOU'RE EVEN DUMBER THAN I
THOUGHT. - WHAT WAS THAT?

467
00:21:51,333 --> 00:21:53,000
- IT'S TIME FOR YOU AND ME

468
00:21:53,083 --> 00:21:56,625
TO SETTLE THIS LITTLE RIVALRY
ONCE AND FOR ALL.

469
00:21:56,708 --> 00:21:59,750
- WHAT ARE YOU TALKIN' ABOUT?
- JEEZ, YOU'RE SLOW.

470
00:21:59,833 --> 00:22:02,666
I'M SAYIN' I'M TIRED
OF ALWAYS FOLLOWING YOUR LEAD.

471
00:22:02,750 --> 00:22:05,333
NOW I'LL FOLLOW
MY OWN PATH.

472
00:22:05,416 --> 00:22:08,541
AS OF THIS MOMENT,
I'M THROUGH WITH FAIRY TAIL.

473
00:22:08,625 --> 00:22:10,916
AND I'M THROUGH
WITH ALL OF YOU.

474
00:22:11,000 --> 00:22:13,125
- YOU'RE SERIOUS?
- YES YES.

475
00:22:13,208 --> 00:22:14,833
THAT'S WHAT I CALL A MAN.

476
00:22:14,916 --> 00:22:17,291
MY DARLING ICE-CUBE REALLY KNOWS
HOW TO WARM ME UP.

477
00:22:17,375 --> 00:22:21,041
NOW BE A DEAR AND FETCH ME
A DRAGON SLAYER,

478
00:22:21,125 --> 00:22:23,291
WOULD YOU?

479
00:22:23,375 --> 00:22:26,458
- YOU DON'T WANT TO DO THIS,
GRAY.

480
00:22:26,541 --> 00:22:29,916
- IF YOU REALLY BELIEVE THAT,
STAY THERE.

481
00:22:30,000 --> 00:22:32,958
IT'LL BE MUCH EASIER
TO END YOU!

482
00:22:35,625 --> 00:22:38,750
- ( end theme playing )

483
00:22:48,666 --> 00:22:52,458
- ( singing in Japanese )

484
00:24:12,583 --> 00:24:14,625
- Happy: WHO DO YOU THINK
WOULD WIN IN A FIGHT?

485
00:24:14,708 --> 00:24:16,916
- YOU OR GRAY? 
- Natsu: ME, OF COURSE.

486
00:24:17,000 --> 00:24:17,875
THERE'S NO WAY
SIR STRIPS-A-LOT'S

487
00:24:17,958 --> 00:24:19,125
GONNA BRING ME DOWN.

488
00:24:19,208 --> 00:24:20,875
- REALLY? 'CAUSE HE JUST
SAID, "THERE'S NO WAY

489
00:24:20,958 --> 00:24:23,125
THAT PINK-HAIRED FLAME MUNCHER
WILL EVER BEAT ME."

490
00:24:23,208 --> 00:24:25,833
- SAY WHAT? IT'S NOT PINK,
IT'S LIGHTISH RED.

491
00:24:25,916 --> 00:24:28,500
THAT NO GOOD, BOXER DROPPING,
