492
00:24:28,583 --> 00:24:30,666
- IT'S NOT AN INSULT CONTEST.

493
00:24:30,750 --> 00:24:33,250
- ( Happy and Natsu speaking )

494
00:24:33,333 --> 00:24:35,333
- Happy: THE SIZE OF THE INSULT
DOESN'T MATTER.

495
00:24:35,416 --> 00:24:37,500
REMEMBER,
BREVITY IS THE SOUL OF WIT.

496
00:24:37,583 --> 00:24:39,166
- Natsu: HE STINKS!

497
00:24:39,250 --> 00:24:41,875
- WELL, I GUESS IT WAS
PRETTY BRIEF, AT LEAST.

